data.description: Sellers offering $10,000 in concessions for rate buy down!! Fantastic home just 10 minutes outside of Surprise. This bright, open floorplan is one of the biggest in the neighborhood and has been beautifully updated throughout. The kitchen features a large island, farmhouse style sink, and new granite countertops. Upstairs includes a large loft, 4 spacious bedrooms with new carpet, and a beautiful master bedroom with en suite and huge walk-in closet. All floors updated in 2022!! The oversized backyard is perfect for entertaining, with a covered patio, well designed landscaping and no neighbors behind you! Other features include a separate laundry room with extra storage and utility sink, a 3 car garage with epoxy floors and attached storage cabinets. Don't miss this desert oasis!!!
